This is a school project for Bezier curve editor.

Demo control:
Esc, Ctrl-Q				Exit
Left click				Move control point
Middle click or Ctrl-Right click	Add control point
Right click				Remove control point
R					Reset camera
C					Toggle de Casteljau/Bernstein algorithm
P					Render control polygon
+/=					Increase the slices rendered
-/_					Decrease the slices rendered

Camera control:
Alt-Left click				Pan camera
Alt-Right click				Zoom camera

Homepage: http://github.com/skaslev/bezier/
Author: Slavomir Kaslev <slavomir.kaslev@gmail.com>
